<hack name="TRM and TRX" author="Cyber(?), periwinkle">
	<panel>
	<field type="info">
		Adds &lt;TRM, which is like &lt;TRA but preserves x and y velocity,
		and &lt;TRX, which is like &lt;TRM but also preserves x and y position.
		For &lt;TRX, only use two arguments (The Map ID and Event Number).
		Rewritten from the original hack by (presumably) Cyber, as that hack had
		a few bugs with it.
